  "texts": [
    "In this work, further real-life tests should conducted.",
    "The work of Lyu and Shu (2021) is also part of the medical domain, more specifically in 3D brain tumor detection and segmentation.",
    "They, inspired by the winners of Multimodal Brain Tumor Segmentation Challenge (BraTS) 2018 (Myronenko 2019), created a two-stage cascade network, which provides quantitative and qualitative improvements for model ensembling and stabilizes the predictions.",
    "The first stage calculates rough segmentation, while the second stage concatenates preliminary maps from the first stage and MRI input and refines the results.",
    "Attention-gates (AGs) (Oktay et al. 2018) are used to suppress irrelevant background data."
  ],
